title: Life Lessons from the Road: "I'm a Cowboy Now"
itunes:title: Life Lessons from the Road: "I'm a Cowboy Now"
description:
Rachel Bonnetta and company are back for a brand new episode! Rachel, broadcasting from her mom's basement in Toronto after completing a week-long road trip across the country, recaps the best sights and sounds from her journey. We also dig into some NFL headlines, including Tyreek Hill saying that Tua Tagovailoa is a more accurate passer than Patrick Mahomes, Jason Garrett joining NBC's football coverage, and Kliff Kingsbury literally praying that Kyler Murray's new deal will be done before training camp. Rachel delivers some life lessons learned from the road before eliminating another team from the Benched Bachelorette sweepstakes.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
